name: Beni
description: Beni Is A Memecoin Based On Coinbase Director's Pet Dog, Launched On The Base Blockchain. It Aims To Create A Fun, Engaging, And Inclusive Community For Crypto Enthusiasts And Pet Lovers. Built On The Solid Foundation Of Base, Beni Enjoys The Benefits Of A Secure, Scalable, And User-Friendly Blockchain. This Paw-Some Memecoin Is Designed To Be Accessible To Everyone, From Seasoned Crypto Traders To Newcomers Who Are Just Starting Their Journey In The World Of Digital Assets.
